00:03:41.460 --> 00:03:46.880
ease of use translates directly
into less calls to the help desk,

00:03:46.880 --> 00:03:47.410
etc.

00:03:47.460 --> 00:03:53.460
But innovation in the IT world also
translates into ease of deployment.

00:03:53.460 --> 00:03:56.460
Ease of management.

00:03:56.460 --> 00:04:01.460
Ultimately translates into
lower total cost of ownership.

00:04:01.460 --> 00:04:04.690
And that's where we focus our
innovation and our skills at

00:04:04.700 --> 00:04:07.460
innovation in the IT world.

00:04:07.700 --> 00:04:10.460
Both in the software and in the hardware.

