00:33:27.280 --> 00:33:33.860
Be able to look at the books that are
overdue and also alert students as to the

00:33:33.860 --> 00:33:35.580
new books that are available in library.

00:33:35.660 --> 00:33:40.030
And finally the little bitty
handy helpers which go a long way.

00:33:40.040 --> 00:33:46.620
I think in schools we have some very
large volumes of binders of information

00:33:46.960 --> 00:33:48.890
which deal with policies and procedures.

00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:52.270
We're able to quickly give our students,
teachers, and parents,

00:33:52.270 --> 00:33:56.060
and administrators the policies
at their fingertips all with

00:33:56.070 --> 00:33:58.300
the push of a function key.

00:33:58.530 --> 00:34:00.810
So in closing,
I think I would like to call to

00:34:00.810 --> 00:34:04.960
action all the developers out here
