or other system management monitors.

00:34:27.760 --> 00:34:32.150
Being able to look at your KPIs,
or being able to quickly monitor

00:34:32.150 --> 00:34:34.240
your hosted applications.

00:34:34.240 --> 00:34:39.660
Looking at bandwidth and looking at
effective utilization and availability.

00:34:39.660 --> 00:34:42.780
And finally,
with presence awareness and also

00:34:42.780 --> 00:34:47.290
looking at hardware integration widgets,
you're able to manage and

00:34:47.290 --> 00:34:49.480
monitor your whole enterprise.

00:34:49.480 --> 00:34:53.620
So in a nutshell,
what we see here is we have

00:34:53.620 --> 00:34:59.170
achieved our goal of enhancing,
or increasing the utilization of

00:34:59.230 --> 00:35:01.360
technology all with Apple products.

00:35:01.360 --> 00:35:06.300
And I'm very happy to say that we are
the leading technology school district

00:35:06.470 --> 00:35:09.110
and we plan on being there forever.

00:35:09.170 --> 00:35:10.910
Thank you.

00:35:20.320 --> 00:35:25.310
Well thank you Vijay and I'm sure
that any of you who are in Fortune 500

00:35:25.420 --> 00:35:31.070
IT shops find a lot of this very
